This is very good although I made quite a few changes. I used sesame oil and also (after tasting the sauce and finding it VERY sour) I added a LOT more sugar. Not sure how much, maybe a quarter cup. Also only used three scallions although could have gone up a little on those. But I think 1.5 cups would have been overkill. As I made it it's very refreshing, healthy side.

