Rating: 3
Before making the receipe, I noticed that it contained soy sauce and 3/4 tsp. of salt. The salt amount seemed to be too much, so I only used 1/4 tsp. instead and it was the correct amount. If I had used the amount recommended in the recipe, it would have been inedible. Instead, it was terrific and it will be a summer staple.